title: Refactored alarmManager:
message:
Refactored alarmManager:

A new alarm is now set every time an event happens, like an old alarm went off.
Therfore only one alarm is set up at a time. Not multiple as before. Also
the setup timer that whent off every day is therfore not nececeary anymore.
